De Praeparatione p. 126. Freiburg. N. p. 1080: Lond. xxvii. 13: 24 September <1532>. LB. App. 368.

[A year-date can be assigned. both from the letter to which this is an answer and from the contents of this letter. Erasinus had just finished the second edition of the Apopktheymata (1532) and was preparing a new edition of the Adaqia, which appeared in March 1533.]
